      <title>纽约联储发现1月份供应链压力略有上升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/new-york-fed-finds-slightly-higher-supply-chain-pressure-january-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行周二发布的一份报告称，供应链压力有所上升，但在今年年初仍然相当低，这表明与中东问题相关的航运中断尚未在普遍中断中显现出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/new-york-fed-finds-slightly-higher-supply-chain-pressure-january-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:24:51 GMT</pubDate>
