      <title>耶伦表示国会应授权监管稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yellen-says-congress-should-provide-authority-regulate-stablecoins-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周二告诉立法者，国会应提供联邦权力来监管稳定币发行者和钱包提供商，以缩小消费者保护和金融稳定保护方面的差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yellen-says-congress-should-provide-authority-regulate-stablecoins-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 16:13:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
