      <title>随着经济衰退扩大，纽约社区银行股票价值将减半</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/new-york-community-bancorp-stock-value-set-halve-slump-extends-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 的股价周二又下跌 9%，自该银行上周公布意外季度亏损以来，抛售进一步扩大，并导致该股在当前水平上市值将缩水一半以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/new-york-community-bancorp-stock-value-set-halve-slump-extends-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 15:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
